title: The Clumsys.rar
description:
Tim and his mischievous friends have got themselves into quite a pickle when they discovered Grandpas latest invention...The Time Machine. Help Grandpa track down 20 kids lost in time and clean up any traces of the future that they left behind.

Find the hidden objects left behind to avoid disaster...who knows what kind of devastating chain reaction a toy car could cause in the year 200BC. Play 100 levels and four unique gameplay modes.
